<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.1">
<l>iruntaṇ mānila mēṉama tāyvaḷai maruppiṉi lakattoṭukki</l>
<l>karuntaṇ mākaṭal kaṇṭuyiṉ ṟavaṉiṭaṅ kamalanaṉ malarttēṟal</l>
<l>arunti yiṉṉicai muraṉṟeḻu maḷikulam potuḷiyam poḻilūṭē</l>
<l>cerunti nāṇmalar ceṉṟaṇain tuḻitaru tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of him who sleeps in the great sea, dark and cool,</l>
<l>Having, as a boar, deposited onto his curved tusk,</l>
<l rend="indent">the great earth, vast and cool,</l>
<l>Is Tiruvayintirapuram where the day’s flowers [from] the pear [tree] drift,</l>
<l rend="indent">passing [then] touching, in the midst of a lovely grove,</l>
<l>Accompanied by a swarm of bees which arise, humming sweet music</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] drinking honey from the fine lotus blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
